<div class="thumbinner" style="width:302px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Drifting1.JPG" class="image" title="A Toyota Supra in drifting exhibition in Atlanta in 2005."><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/49/Drifting1.JPG/300px-Drifting1.JPG" width="300" height="225" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
